fields.Title: WHIRLING F1 / INDUSTRIAL STOVE
fields.Description: You can use the stove to boil the hanged man's boots when Kim is not around.

fields.Title: START
input
Endurance: "This is gonna take *the hard* stuff..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This is gonna take *the hard* stuff too. Use as much as you can.

fields.Title: You: "Beautiful."
fields.Dialogue Text: Beautiful.

fields.Title: You: "Wait..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Wait...

fields.Title: You: "Wait some more..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Wait some more...

fields.Title: You: "Dump the sock and flesh stew -- and..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Dump the sock and flesh stew -- and examine your new boots!

fields.Title: Industrial Stove: "The boots look clean but still smel..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The boots look clean but still smell funky.

fields.Title: Logic: "It's bad with those boots. Don't be..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's bad with those boots. Don't be stingy now.

Industrial Stove: "The whole kitchen now smells like w..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The whole kitchen now smells like white vinegar. But maybe your boots won't smell like a corpse?

fields.Title: Half Light: "You should taste some."
fields.Dialogue Text: You should taste some.

fields.Title: Industrial Stove: "This industrial gas-powered stove h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This industrial gas-powered stove has been used to prepare food for many hungry hostel guests. There are several pots and pans on hand.

fields.Title: Half Light: "Yeah, maybe that's a good habit *no..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Yeah, maybe that's a good habit *not* to include in your roster. Anyways, the boots are coming along nicely.

fields.Title: industrialstovemainhub
You: "Check out the cookware."
fields.Dialogue Text: Check out the cookware.

fields.Title: You: "Soap! That's exactly what I need. P..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Soap! That's exactly what I need. Pour lots of dish soap into the pot.

fields.Title: Industrial Stove: "The soap bubbles over the rim of th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The soap bubbles over the rim of the pot -- the water slowly comes to a boil.

fields.Title: You: "Wait *even more*..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Wait *even more*...

fields.Title: IsKimHere()
IsKimHere()
!(IsKimHere())

fields.Dialogue Text: Master chef out. [Leave.]

fields.Title: Industrial Stove: "A two course dinner of rotting fles..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A two course dinner of rotting flesh and hardened ceramic.

fields.Title: Endurance: "Rotten Human Meat-Ceramic Boot Soup..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Rotten Human Meat-Ceramic Boot Soup? Nope, you really shouldn't.

fields.Title: You: "Add water -- and the boots -- to th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Add water -- and the boots -- to the pot. Bring it all to a *nice* boil.

fields.Title: Industrial Stove: "The strong smell of vinegar forces..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The strong smell of vinegar forces you to step away from the pot. The water slowly comes to a boil.

fields.Title: Industrial Stove: "The strong vinegar odour forces you..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The strong vinegar odour forces you to take a few steps back from the stove.

fields.Title: Encyclopedia: "Well, at least now you know."
fields.Dialogue Text: Well, at least now you know.

fields.Title: You: "Endure the stench. It has to come o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Endure the stench. It has to come out eventually, right?

fields.Title: Jump to: [industrialstovemainhub]
Jump to: [Industrial Stove: "That's it, chef! The boots are as c..."]
Savoir Faire: "Getting the corpse residue out of t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Getting the corpse residue out of these boots is going to require patience. And also a huge pot full of boiling water, soap, and white vinegar.

fields.Title: Industrial Stove: "Strips of polymer fabric and human..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Strips of polymer fabric and human tissue separate from the lining of the boots. They float to the bubbling surface.

fields.Title: Industrial Stove: "The bottom of the pot fills with sh..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The bottom of the pot fills with shiny white goo.

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "Far away, in the darkness of a make..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Far away, in the darkness of a makeshift morgue behind Station 41's lazareth, Dr. Nix Gottlieb cuts into the cold, dead feet of a murder victim. The veins are oddly black, he suspects a neurotoxin...

fields.Title: You: "No way, I'm not touching it."
fields.Dialogue Text: No way, I'm not touching it.

fields.Title: Industrial Stove: "Few more moments and the boots will..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Few more moments and the boots will be ready.

fields.Title: Jump to: [You: "A little more..."]
Industrial Stove: "The stove is unmoved by your coming..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The stove is unmoved by your comings and goings.

fields.Title: Industrial Stove: "A commercial pot draws your attenti..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A commercial pot draws your attention. It's very large. Gigantic, even. It could be used to make enough stew to feed an entire city. And also to boil a putrid pair of death-boots.

fields.Title: Industrial Stove: "The boots look cleaner and cleaner...."
fields.Dialogue Text: The boots look cleaner and cleaner. Those bits of human flesh are beginning to look *cooked*. You can smell it too.

fields.Title: You: "All right! Dump the water and sniff..."
fields.Dialogue Text: All right! Dump the water and sniff the boots.

fields.Title: Conceptualization: "Of course it tastes vile. Look at t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Of course it tastes vile. Look at the effort you put in the culinary side of this? Not exactly fine dining, is it?

fields.Title: Savoir Faire: "The lieutenant said you'd need to b..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant said you'd need to boil the boots in acid to get the corpse smell out, but this huge pot, industrial dish soap, white vinegar, and patience might do the trick.

fields.Title: You: "Check out the cleaning supplies."
fields.Dialogue Text: Check out the cleaning supplies.

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "Whatever you had planned, you have..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Whatever you had planned, you have to do it when the lieutenant's gone.

fields.Title: Volition: "You're tasting another human being...."
fields.Dialogue Text: You're tasting another human being. You shouldn't.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""What are you planning to do, throw..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What are you planning to do, throw a dinner party? Please refrain from culinary experiments until after we've finished the investigation."

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "You have awakened the *hunger*. The..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You have awakened the *hunger*. There is no turning back now, better invest in a good cook book and stock up on salt.

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "Feels like you should've used vineg..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Feels like you should've used vinegar too...

fields.Title: Jump to: [industrialstovemainhub]
Industrial Stove: "The scorching hot 'stew' burns your..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The scorching hot 'stew' burns your finger and tastes absolutely vile.

fields.Title: Industrial Stove: "Your hands are protected from the h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Your hands are protected from the heat, but the 'stew' tastes absolutely vile.

fields.Title: You: "A little more..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A little more...

fields.Title: Industrial Stove: "That's it, chef! The boots are as c..."
fields.Dialogue Text: That's it, chef! The boots are as clean as they're going to get. Steam dense with the smell of strange meat disappears into the vent above the stove.

fields.Title: Perception (Smell): "Just like beef stew."
fields.Dialogue Text: Just like beef stew.

fields.Title: You: "The boots are *really* disgusting...."
fields.Dialogue Text: The boots are *really* disgusting. Pour some dish soap *and* the bottle of white vinegar into the pot.

fields.Title: Industrial Stove: "A pair of real beauties! The boots..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A pair of real beauties! The boots are shiny, hot and reek of vinegar. Just perfect.

fields.Title: You: "Dump the sock and flesh stew -- and..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Dump the sock and flesh stew -- and examine your new boots!

Interfacing: "Alright now, chef. Light the stove..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Alright now, chef. Light the stove up and boil them.

fields.Title: Industrial Stove: "There is a variety of soaps and ble..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There is a variety of soaps and bleaches in the cabinet to the left of the stove. There is also a bottle of white vinegar in the cabinet next to the fridge.

fields.Title: Industrial Stove: "A pair of real beauties! The boots..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A pair of real beauties! The boots are shiny, hot and reek of vinegar. Just perfect.

fields.Title: You: "Try boiling them again, this time w..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Try boiling them again, this time with white vinegar.

fields.Title: Industrial Stove: "The delicious smells of cheap soap..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The delicious smells of cheap soap and vinegar waft up from the pot.
